query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS reliability_tests (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  testName VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  testCategory ENUM('central_bank_split', 'fx_gap', 'inflation', 'aid_flows', 'sanctions', 'sector_metrics', 'humanitarian', 'banking', 'trade') NOT NULL,
  questionText TEXT NOT NULL,
  expectedEvidencePattern TEXT,
  expectedSources JSON,
  difficulty ENUM('easy', 'medium', 'hard') DEFAULT 'medium',
  isActive BOOLEAN DEFAULT TRUE,
  createdAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  INDEX idx_category (testCategory),
  INDEX idx_active (isActive)
);
